---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout title="Refund Policy | QuranAble" description="Refund policy for QuranAble students.">
  <div class="bg-slate-50 min-h-screen py-24 md:py-32">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6 bg-white p-10 rounded-[2rem] border border-slate-200 shadow-xl">
      <h1 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-black text-indigo-950 mb-8">Refund Policy</h1>
      <div class="space-y-6 text-slate-600 font-medium leading-relaxed">
        <p>We want you to be completely satisfied with your learning experience at QuranAble. This is why we offer a free trial so you can evaluate our classes risk-free.</p>
        <p>If you subscribe to a paid plan and find that it does not meet your expectations, you may request a full refund within the first 7 days of your paid subscription.</p>
        <p>To request a refund or cancel your subscription, simply contact your academic advisor via WhatsApp or email us.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
